room_title: Escape room "White House Defusal" by Project Panic Dallas in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: A bomb threat has been called within the White House. As a retired Secret Service agent, you are the first to hear about it. However, a trusted source has alerted you that a higher-level government official may be behind this traitorous act. There may even be others who are working against the country. Therefore it is up to you to find a secret way into the White House and accomplish your mission. Will you defuse the bomb and save the country?
